snippet.title: Load Roll Die - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming out October 6th 2021: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1410140/Load_Roll_Die/

Join our discord server here: https://discord.gg/XQNG3uD

Stop, swap and roll your dice in this Roguelite Dice-builder! Steal dice faces from your enemies and use them to create the perfect dice set for taking down your opponents. Roll and combine your dice to create explosions, freeze faces, duplicate dice and more!
